    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior shows significant age and neglect, with visible rust on the rocker panels, several large dents, and clear coat failure across most surfaces. Inside, the cabin requires a deep clean and repair, as the upholstery is heavily torn and several plastic trim pieces are cracked or missing. Mechanically, the car starts but runs roughly, with a noticeable exhaust leak and an illuminated check engine light, meaning it will likely need significant work or a tow to be safely roadworthy.",
